\title{Prerequisites}
\ul{
\li{Familiarity with red teaming concepts and tools}
\li{Access to a test or lab environment for safe execution}
\li{Python 3.8+ with required dependencies installed}
\li{Appropriate authorization for any testing activities}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Objectives}
\ul{
\li{Deploy BloodHound CE server using Docker Compose}
\li{Collect AD data using SharpHound v2 or BloodHound.py}
\li{Import collected data into BloodHound CE for graph analysis}
\li{Identify shortest attack paths from owned principals to Domain Admins}
\li{Discover ACL-based attack paths, Kerberoastable accounts, and delegation abuse}
\li{Execute custom Cypher queries for advanced attack path analysis}
\li{Generate attack path reports for engagement documentation}
}
}

